name: CompareChecker
overview:
CompareChecker allows UK consumers to search multiple car insurance price comparison sites at the click of a button.

The consumer saves time and money through effortless access to greater market coverage.

It also offers comparison sites a low cost acquisition platform and exposure of their offering to apathetic consumers who otherwise would not use more than one site.
